Pool:
vmImage (Microsoft-hosted agent) → Defines pre-built agent image like ubuntu-latest, windows-latest.
name (self-hosted pool) → Specifies custom agent pool created in Azure DevOps.
demands → Ensures pipeline runs only on agents matching specific capabilities (e.g., docker installed).
container → Runs job inside a container instead of host machine.

